{"tid":600852,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Dyson風筒電壓問題","createTime":"2018-03-21T16:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:31:23.000Z","uid":31990,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7e65ecdc6c8987abe3409eb7fa6e01d5ebfa40","tid":600852,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"幾個月前買左個水貨用,開頭用d濕鳩旅行轉換插,用左1個月左右個插壞左,拖板上面都有熔熔地既痕跡<br />\n<br />\n跟住換左個有fuse既轉插,用左幾個月都無咩事,啱啱再用吹吹下停左<br />\n<br />\n跟住望到個轉插無著燈,換過第個轉插又work返,跟住我望下風筒個插頭,發覺有d野熔撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個情況係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  剪斷佢換香港3腳插得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係要落鴨記買變壓器? 但佢寫住100V~250V<br />\n<br />\n求解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3ylT4mr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3ylT4mr.jpg&h=b7afa5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/61ICTkR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F61ICTkR.jpg&h=8856eb5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"338267907b6998c4bb8f4c6b80aab7e662d4dd80","tid":600852,"uid":137275,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"差個幾舊水.何必呢"},{"pid":"dcbede3377589f7a6a6e38582bdb1fa4ce926b9d","tid":600852,"uid":14441,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"唔洗買火牛 買個好啲轉插就得 應該插唔實搶火"},{"pid":"818b2a834011a87e2c9552c71436ca812a2022be","tid":600852,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"338267907b6998c4bb8f4c6b80aab